::Kaiser::
       He smirks inwardly at this new warrior.  Yes, adequate suits him. But 
he likes it not.  Methinks, perhaps, he needs a lesson.  He grins again and 
looks over to Major Tyrael.  "He seems dissatisfied with my compliment, 
Major."  He gestures at Deathsteel with one hand.  "May I?"
